that  they  didn’t  have  an  R&D  department,  and  they  seemed  sort
of  proud  of  it  that  they  didn’t  have  one.  And  I  guess  it  is  because
they  didn’t  want  to  say  to  the  PSC  that  we  got  all  this  in  our  cost
