FUNDING  OPPORTUNITY  ANNOUNCEMENT  (FOA),’’  attached  to  e-mail  entitled  ‘‘FG  Q&As
for Final FOA.6–23–08.v4.doc’’ from Jarad Daniels to Keith Miles and Thomas Sarkus, June 23,
3008.

